They have things in here that

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:12.160
are

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:15.269
bad. I see the hazard

00:13:15.279 --> 00:13:19.269
symbol again; it looks like a

00:13:19.279 --> 00:13:23.030
device with a yellow hazard symbol on

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:24.949
the side of it. Do you

00:13:24.959 --> 00:13:27.590
remember what I told you about

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:30.389
the purple dragon

00:13:30.389 --> 00:13:30.399
coming

00:13:30.399 --> 00:13:33.190
up three times out of the water

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:36.150
by Cuba? Again, I see the

00:13:36.160 --> 00:13:39.110
hazard symbol—the yellow with

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:41.990
the black design on it. That's what

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:44.389
I'm seeing on the side of a device

00:13:44.389 --> 00:13:44.399
in an

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:46.710
underground bunker, and it came

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:49.110
from Russia. They got it from Russia for

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:51.269
trade for something. They're doing

00:13:51.279 --> 00:13:53.350
something, but it's

00:13:53.350 --> 00:13:53.360
underground

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:56.150
in

00:13:56.150 --> 00:13:56.160
a

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:58.949
cave on the island,

00:13:58.949 --> 00:13:58.959
and

00:13:58.959 --> 00:14:02.550
it has little wires and a little red

00:14:02.560 --> 00:14:05.590
antenna on it. They only have

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:09.350
one of them.

00:14:09.360 --> 00:14:11.590
That's all they need is one. They just

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:15.030
want you to store it there. I see these

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:18.389
islands, but this is like the mainland

00:14:18.399 --> 00:14:20.790
and they're all highlighted with

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:25.590
red. This concerns Cuba.

00:14:25.590 --> 00:14:25.600
I see those

00:14:25.600 --> 00:14:28.230
islands and they're red, and

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:30.470
it's about England. But I'm seeing

00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:33.829
Russia is involved in this

00:14:33.829 --> 00:14:33.839
in

00:14:33.839 --> 00:14:36.389
retaliation. There's a

00:14:36.399 --> 00:14:37.990
device that they're putting in

00:14:37.990 --> 00:14:38.000
storage

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:40.150
in Cuba. Why do they want to

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:43.110
store it in Cuba? It makes you purple. I

00:14:43.120 --> 00:14:45.590
just saw it; I had a flash of it and it

00:14:45.600 --> 00:14:48.389
looked purple. It makes them purple when

00:14:48.389 --> 00:14:48.399
they

00:14:48.399 --> 00:14:51.350
die.

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:53.750
It's like the

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:57.269
girl in Willy Wonka

00:14:57.269 --> 00:14:57.279
who

00:14:57.279 --> 00:14:58.790
turned her face blue because she ate the

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:00.949
blueberry, Violet. That's basically

00:15:00.959 --> 00:15:02.470
what I'm seeing: these people are

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:04.949
dead and it's making them purple.

00:15:07.680 --> 00:15:10.310
I saw attacks coming against

00:15:10.320 --> 00:15:11.990
America.

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:15.750
I saw old Cuban alliances

00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:19.030
trying to bring back old ties,

00:15:19.040 --> 00:15:22.550
trying to bring forth a third world war

00:15:22.560 --> 00:15:24.949
greater than what we've ever seen before

00:15:24.959 --> 00:15:27.990
with conventional weapons beyond what

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:30.550
they ever had in World War II and World

00:15:30.560 --> 00:15:34.710
War I. Missiles that will destroy mass

00:15:34.710 --> 00:15:34.720
amounts

00:15:34.720 --> 00:15:36.790
of people.

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:39.829
Not just like

00:15:39.829 --> 00:15:39.839
HIMARS,

00:15:39.839 --> 00:15:43.670
we're talking bombs that are crazy

00:15:43.680 --> 00:15:45.189
compared to what they had in World War

00:15:45.199 --> 00:15:48.629
II. Our technology now is scary

00:15:48.639 --> 00:15:50.470
with biological weapons and all the stuff we

00:15:50.480 --> 00:15:53.189
have. And when they try to do all this,

00:15:53.199 --> 00:15:56.399
it will be very, very ugly.

